title: 'The Bachelorette' New Season in Black & White
text:
" The Bachelorette " will offer Rachel Lindsay clear choices ... if race is a factor.
The photo was snapped behind the scenes on the first night of taping, showing 12 contestants, and there is a mix ... but looks like she's trending black.
It's pretty clear from the finale of "The Bachelor" ... producers are going to make race a central story line ... looks like mission accomplished.
